These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
Music-Genre: rock, blues, salsa, house
1. Music-Genre:blues is between Music-Genre:salsa and Music-Genre:house##2
2. Music-Genre:blues is on the left of Music-Genre:salsa##1
3. Music-Genre:rock is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | rock | house | blues | salsa |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
Beverage: coffee, lemonade, water, juice
1. Beverage:juice is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:water is on the right of Beverage:coffee##1
3. Beverage:juice is between Beverage:lemonade and Beverage:coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | juice | coffee | water |

 #################################
 
